latestPosts.caption:
Throwback to my very first break on Tv as an Actor. Feeling blessed that in my very first few months of being in the city of dream - Mumbai i got this opportunity to play a part in serial like Anupamaa @starplus . I had never imagined that i will be the part of this show which is loved my millions of people plus for me it was not just a show , it was an emotion because me and my family used to watch this show together when i was in my hometown. So when i became the part of this show it automatically became my biggest achievement till date.❤️
Not only this show gave me the insight of how everything happens on the set but also gave me the the much needed confidence that i can act .✨

Firstly i want to thank @garry_casting_company  sir for being so supportive and helpful .🥰
Thank you @jeetrdchaudhary sir for your trust .😇
Thank you so much @rajan.shahi.543 sir for having faith in me and giving an opportunity to this new comer who had no work experience in serials .❤️

Here , i also want to thank @gauravkhannaofficial sir and @rupaliganguly Ma’am for making sure that i feel like home on the sets and for being motivating ✨it was a dream come true moment for me.😭
And yes thank you @nishisaxenaa for handling my goof-ups .😋

Cheers to my “First”🥂🎉❤️
